description: The request is for a collection of images, each depicting a cat. The defining characteristic of this collection is that the cats should exhibit a variety of different coat colors.

images.prompt: A photorealistic ginger tabby cat lounging in a sunbeam, detailed fur, bright eyes, warm lighting, depth of field
A sleek black cat with emerald green eyes perched on a velvet cushion, low-key lighting, dramatic shadows, high resolution
A calico cat exploring a vibrant garden, detailed flower textures, soft focus background, natural lighting, playful expression
A long-haired Siamese cat with piercing blue eyes sleeping on a cozy blanket, intricate fur patterns, shallow depth of field, indoor setting
